WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.936 align:middle line:90%


00:00:01.936 --> 00:00:05.324 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:05.324 --> 00:00:21.660 align:middle line:90%


00:00:21.660 --> 00:00:25.125 align:middle line:90%
[THROAT SINGING]

00:00:25.125 --> 00:00:54.650 align:middle line:90%


00:00:54.650 --> 00:00:57.410 align:middle line:90%
>> I was eight.

00:00:57.410 --> 00:00:59.900 align:middle line:84%
My parents came home
from the hospital

00:00:59.900 --> 00:01:03.460 align:middle line:90%
and said Dorothy is dead.

00:01:03.460 --> 00:01:05.890 align:middle line:90%
My sister is dead.

00:01:05.890 --> 00:01:09.010 align:middle line:84%
Someone turned off
the light within me.

00:01:09.010 --> 00:01:11.380 align:middle line:90%
It was pitch black.

00:01:11.380 --> 00:01:13.480 align:middle line:90%
Why life?

00:01:13.480 --> 00:01:16.480 align:middle line:84%
How can I accept
the unacceptable?

00:01:16.480 --> 00:01:17.590 align:middle line:90%
My quest has begun.

00:01:17.590 --> 00:01:20.929 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:01:20.929 --> 00:01:29.565 align:middle line:90%


00:01:29.565 --> 00:01:32.956 align:middle line:90%
[PEOPLE CHANTING]

00:01:32.956 --> 00:01:50.316 align:middle line:90%


00:01:50.316 --> 00:01:53.788 align:middle line:90%
[BELL RINGING]

00:01:53.788 --> 00:02:10.590 align:middle line:90%


00:02:10.590 --> 00:02:13.320 align:middle line:84%
Since she died, I
have pretended to be

00:02:13.320 --> 00:02:20.010 align:middle line:84%
alive to the joys, worries,
and pleasures of everyday life.

00:02:20.010 --> 00:02:23.800 align:middle line:84%
Despite the years that have gone
by, I see that I cannot live

00:02:23.800 --> 00:02:26.520 align:middle line:84%
with her, and I cannot
live without her.

00:02:26.520 --> 00:02:37.905 align:middle line:90%


00:02:37.905 --> 00:02:39.390 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

00:02:39.390 --> 00:02:43.350 align:middle line:90%
Thank you very much.

00:02:43.350 --> 00:02:45.825 align:middle line:90%
[SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:02:45.825 --> 00:02:54.610 align:middle line:90%


00:02:54.610 --> 00:02:59.010 align:middle line:84%
A Tibetan friend, Jampa,
told me about the Buddha

00:02:59.010 --> 00:03:00.750 align:middle line:84%
and his first teaching
on the Four Noble

00:03:00.750 --> 00:03:04.740 align:middle line:84%
Truths that are supposed
to free from suffering.

00:03:04.740 --> 00:03:08.160 align:middle line:84%
He also told me about an
ancient ritual which leads

00:03:08.160 --> 00:03:11.230 align:middle line:90%
to serenity and enlightenment.

00:03:11.230 --> 00:03:14.400 align:middle line:84%
Kalachakra was getting
into resonance with me.

00:03:14.400 --> 00:03:16.620 align:middle line:84%
That is what led
me to Dharamshala,

00:03:16.620 --> 00:03:20.190 align:middle line:84%
this uncommon Indian city
where the Tibetans live happily

00:03:20.190 --> 00:03:23.207 align:middle line:84%
and joyfully despite
the pain of exile.

00:03:23.207 --> 00:03:24.870 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:03:24.870 --> 00:04:35.600 align:middle line:90%


00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:40.580 align:middle line:84%
>> I am happy and worried,
as often, I am unsatisfied.

00:04:40.580 --> 00:04:43.190 align:middle line:90%


00:04:43.190 --> 00:04:48.150 align:middle line:84%
Deep down inside me, I still
miss Dorothy's presence.

00:04:48.150 --> 00:04:51.140 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes I pretend
to laugh, to have fun.

00:04:51.140 --> 00:05:03.300 align:middle line:90%


00:05:03.300 --> 00:06:29.615 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:06:29.615 --> 00:06:30.977 align:middle line:10%
[SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:06:30.977 --> 00:06:44.493 align:middle line:90%


00:06:44.493 --> 00:06:45.626 align:middle line:90%
>> Excuse me.

00:06:45.626 --> 00:06:48.499 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

00:06:48.499 --> 00:06:49.540 align:middle line:10%
>> What's happening here?

00:06:49.540 --> 00:06:51.250 align:middle line:10%
Some preparation?

00:06:51.250 --> 00:06:53.260 align:middle line:10%
Something special?

00:06:53.260 --> 00:06:54.540 align:middle line:10%
>> This is Kalachakra Temple.

00:06:54.540 --> 00:06:58.040 align:middle line:10%
And they are preparing
for a Kalachakra ritual.

00:06:58.040 --> 00:07:16.240 align:middle line:90%


00:07:16.240 --> 00:07:17.910 align:middle line:10%
>> Is this the
Kalachakra statue?

00:07:17.910 --> 00:07:18.710 align:middle line:10%
>> Yes, yes.

00:07:18.710 --> 00:07:28.740 align:middle line:90%


00:07:28.740 --> 00:07:30.940 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

00:07:30.940 --> 00:07:34.335 align:middle line:90%


00:07:34.335 --> 00:07:35.710 align:middle line:10%
>> What does the
young monk want?

00:07:35.710 --> 00:07:38.350 align:middle line:10%


00:07:38.350 --> 00:07:41.940 align:middle line:10%
>> He's interested in
Kalachakra teaching.

00:07:41.940 --> 00:07:43.633 align:middle line:90%
>> [CHUCKLING]

00:07:43.633 --> 00:07:46.459 align:middle line:90%


00:07:46.459 --> 00:07:48.110 align:middle line:10%
But he's very young.

00:07:48.110 --> 00:07:50.750 align:middle line:10%
>> He's very young, yes.

00:07:50.750 --> 00:07:51.550 align:middle line:10%
Thank you so much.

00:07:51.550 --> 00:07:52.250 align:middle line:10%
>> OK, welcome.

00:07:52.250 --> 00:07:53.050 align:middle line:10%
>> Goodbye.

00:07:53.050 --> 00:07:54.030 align:middle line:10%
Thank you.

00:07:54.030 --> 00:07:54.830 align:middle line:90%
Goodbye.

00:07:54.830 --> 00:08:00.480 align:middle line:90%


00:08:00.480 --> 00:08:03.980 align:middle line:84%
Jampa will introduce me
to Thamthog Rinpoche,

00:08:03.980 --> 00:08:07.380 align:middle line:84%
the abbot of the monastery
of the Dalai Lama.

00:08:07.380 --> 00:08:09.500 align:middle line:84%
He is believed to
be the reincarnation

00:08:09.500 --> 00:08:12.140 align:middle line:90%
of a great master.

00:08:12.140 --> 00:08:15.540 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:08:15.540 --> 00:08:18.200 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

00:08:18.200 --> 00:08:19.530 align:middle line:10%
It's very nice to meet you.

00:08:19.530 --> 00:08:21.270 align:middle line:10%
I'm so honored to meet you.

00:08:21.270 --> 00:08:22.250 align:middle line:10%
>> Thank you, me too.

00:08:22.250 --> 00:08:24.130 align:middle line:10%
>> You're the abbot
of this monastery?

00:08:24.130 --> 00:08:25.260 align:middle line:10%
>> Yes.

00:08:25.260 --> 00:08:26.450 align:middle line:10%
>> Since how long?

00:08:26.450 --> 00:08:28.820 align:middle line:10%
>> Four years.

00:08:28.820 --> 00:08:29.620 align:middle line:10%
>> Nice.

00:08:29.620 --> 00:08:31.720 align:middle line:10%
>> And where are you from?

00:08:31.720 --> 00:08:32.870 align:middle line:10%
>> I'm from France.

00:08:32.870 --> 00:08:34.335 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, bonjour.

00:08:34.335 --> 00:08:35.135 align:middle line:90%
>> Bonjour.

00:08:35.135 --> 00:08:39.199 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:08:39.199 --> 00:08:42.639 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

00:08:42.639 --> 00:08:45.780 align:middle line:84%
>> You are very
interested in Kalachakra?

00:08:45.780 --> 00:08:47.300 align:middle line:10%
>> Yes.

00:08:47.300 --> 00:09:24.222 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

00:09:24.222 --> 00:09:27.694 align:middle line:90%
[MONKS CHANTING]

00:09:27.694 --> 00:10:32.220 align:middle line:90%


00:10:32.220 --> 00:10:41.606 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:10:41.606 --> 00:10:46.220 align:middle line:84%
>> All this is wonderful,
even intriguing.

00:10:46.220 --> 00:10:50.040 align:middle line:84%
But I still feel lonely, cut
off from myself and the joy

00:10:50.040 --> 00:10:53.030 align:middle line:84%
that this spectacle
could bring me.

00:10:53.030 --> 00:10:56.450 align:middle line:84%
I can feel my ignorance, which
is certainly the underlying

00:10:56.450 --> 00:10:59.390 align:middle line:90%
cause of my suffering.

00:10:59.390 --> 00:11:36.648 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

00:11:36.648 --> 00:11:40.134 align:middle line:90%
[MONKS CHANTING]

00:11:40.134 --> 00:12:13.900 align:middle line:90%


00:12:13.900 --> 00:12:45.654 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

00:12:45.654 --> 00:12:49.133 align:middle line:90%
[MAN'S VOICE OVER CROWD]

00:12:49.133 --> 00:13:05.534 align:middle line:90%


00:13:05.534 --> 00:13:07.522 align:middle line:90%
[BIRD CHIRPING]

00:13:07.522 --> 00:13:13.983 align:middle line:90%


00:13:13.983 --> 00:13:21.438 align:middle line:90%
[BELL RINGING]

00:13:21.438 --> 00:13:24.917 align:middle line:84%
[SINGING BOWLS, DRUMS, THROAT
 SINGING]

00:13:24.917 --> 00:13:32.372 align:middle line:90%


00:13:32.372 --> 00:13:34.360 align:middle line:90%
[FEMALE VOCALS]

00:13:34.360 --> 00:14:02.790 align:middle line:90%


00:14:02.790 --> 00:14:05.990 align:middle line:84%
>> People are coming
from all directions.

00:14:05.990 --> 00:14:10.010 align:middle line:84%
Everyone finds their
place, settles in.

00:14:10.010 --> 00:14:12.740 align:middle line:90%
A fervor begins to develop.

00:14:12.740 --> 00:14:14.330 align:middle line:90%
And the mandala is taking shape.

00:14:14.330 --> 00:14:22.285 align:middle line:90%


00:14:22.285 --> 00:14:25.280 align:middle line:90%
[MONKS CHANTING]

00:14:25.280 --> 00:14:50.702 align:middle line:90%


00:14:50.702 --> 00:14:53.830 align:middle line:90%
[MONKS CHANTING]

00:14:53.830 --> 00:15:41.154 align:middle line:90%


00:15:41.154 --> 00:15:42.648 align:middle line:90%
[CAR HORN]

00:15:42.648 --> 00:15:47.628 align:middle line:90%


00:15:47.628 --> 00:15:49.620 align:middle line:90%
[CAR HORNS]

00:15:49.620 --> 00:17:00.834 align:middle line:90%


00:17:00.834 --> 00:17:02.826 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

00:17:02.826 --> 00:17:06.810 align:middle line:90%


00:17:06.810 --> 00:17:11.150 align:middle line:84%
>> To my great joy, my request,
with the monastery abbot,

00:17:11.150 --> 00:17:15.380 align:middle line:84%
for an audience with the
Dalai Lama has been granted.

00:17:15.380 --> 00:17:18.829 align:middle line:90%
His laughter, his kindness--

00:17:18.829 --> 00:17:24.140 align:middle line:84%
he even says to me, how nice
of you to come and see me.

00:17:24.140 --> 00:17:29.629 align:middle line:84%
When I think of all he has gone
through, I feel very small.

00:17:29.629 --> 00:17:30.545 align:middle line:90%
But I'm still growing.

00:17:30.545 --> 00:17:38.820 align:middle line:90%


00:17:38.820 --> 00:17:43.910 align:middle line:10%
>> I received initiation of
this Kalachakra tantra from

00:17:43.910 --> 00:17:46.370 align:middle line:10%
my senior tutor.

00:17:46.370 --> 00:17:51.250 align:middle line:10%
I also received full
monk's ordination from him.

00:17:51.250 --> 00:17:52.460 align:middle line:10%
He said something like--

00:17:52.460 --> 00:17:56.779 align:middle line:10%
he offered his
students, then me,

00:17:56.779 --> 00:17:58.445 align:middle line:10%
the possibility of
teaching the mandala.

00:17:58.445 --> 00:18:03.290 align:middle line:90%


00:18:03.290 --> 00:18:08.720 align:middle line:10%
Please, now bless him
and carry teaching

00:18:08.720 --> 00:18:16.010 align:middle line:10%
of this tantric teaching to
many people for a long time.

00:18:16.010 --> 00:18:22.130 align:middle line:10%
So while he prayed to
the mandala for me,

00:18:22.130 --> 00:18:24.340 align:middle line:10%
he also was very much moved--

00:18:24.340 --> 00:18:26.000 align:middle line:10%
tears.

00:18:26.000 --> 00:18:28.190 align:middle line:10%
>> Yes.

00:18:28.190 --> 00:18:34.537 align:middle line:10%
>> So now, almost, I
think, 32 or 33 initiations

00:18:34.537 --> 00:18:35.370 align:middle line:10%
of the Kalachakra...

00:18:35.370 --> 00:18:36.590 align:middle line:10%
I've done.

00:18:36.590 --> 00:18:41.060 align:middle line:10%
So I always feel
that's the fulfillment

00:18:41.060 --> 00:18:44.220 align:middle line:10%
of his prayer at that time.

00:18:44.220 --> 00:18:46.700 align:middle line:10%
With very strong--

00:18:46.700 --> 00:18:48.148 align:middle line:10%
[SPEAKING TIBETAN]-- emotion.

00:18:48.148 --> 00:18:51.641 align:middle line:10%
[TIBETAN HORNS]

00:18:51.641 --> 00:18:54.136 align:middle line:90%


00:18:54.136 --> 00:18:57.629 align:middle line:90%
[APPLAUSE]

00:18:57.629 --> 00:19:01.621 align:middle line:90%


00:19:01.621 --> 00:19:05.114 align:middle line:90%
[SNYCHRONIZED CLAPPING]

00:19:05.114 --> 00:19:31.580 align:middle line:90%


00:19:31.580 --> 00:19:37.340 align:middle line:10%
As a Buddhist, this place has
something very sacred place.

00:19:37.340 --> 00:19:44.350 align:middle line:10%
Buddha Shakyamuni achieved
enlightenment of Buddhahood

00:19:44.350 --> 00:19:45.450 align:middle line:10%
in this very place.

00:19:45.450 --> 00:19:48.440 align:middle line:10%


00:19:48.440 --> 00:19:53.380 align:middle line:10%
Of course, everybody
knows Buddha--

00:19:53.380 --> 00:19:58.110 align:middle line:10%
like many other great
teachers, Buddha

00:19:58.110 --> 00:20:03.505 align:middle line:10%
was a symbol of peace,
a symbol of love.

00:20:03.505 --> 00:20:07.855 align:middle line:10%
Now, in such a sacred
place, I am receiving

00:20:07.855 --> 00:20:10.250 align:middle line:10%
Gandhi's granddaughter.

00:20:10.250 --> 00:20:13.700 align:middle line:10%
Very, very special significance.

00:20:13.700 --> 00:20:15.526 align:middle line:10%
I very much appreciate.

00:20:15.526 --> 00:20:16.585 align:middle line:10%
Thank you.

00:20:16.585 --> 00:20:20.050 align:middle line:90%
[APPLAUSE]

00:20:20.050 --> 00:20:24.510 align:middle line:90%


00:20:24.510 --> 00:20:27.732 align:middle line:10%
Now my age is 76.

00:20:27.732 --> 00:20:30.120 align:middle line:10%
But the remainder
of my life, I'm

00:20:30.120 --> 00:20:35.460 align:middle line:10%
totally committed to
non-violence and serving.

00:20:35.460 --> 00:20:39.190 align:middle line:90%


00:20:39.190 --> 00:20:45.422 align:middle line:10%
As a Buddhist practitioner, try
to serve every sentient being,

00:20:45.422 --> 00:20:49.630 align:middle line:10%
and particularly, about
seven billion human beings

00:20:49.630 --> 00:20:51.420 align:middle line:10%
on this planet.

00:20:51.420 --> 00:20:55.950 align:middle line:10%
I'm one of them,
nothing special.

00:20:55.950 --> 00:20:59.300 align:middle line:10%
We are all the
same human beings.

00:20:59.300 --> 00:21:05.474 align:middle line:10%
So non-violence is the
reflection of inner peace.

00:21:05.474 --> 00:21:10.200 align:middle line:10%
The real peaceful world, then,
I think, will be achieved.

00:21:10.200 --> 00:21:12.380 align:middle line:10%
It is possible!

00:21:12.380 --> 00:21:14.560 align:middle line:10%
I think this is the right time.

00:21:14.560 --> 00:21:20.860 align:middle line:10%
Make effort with the vision
to create a better world,

00:21:20.860 --> 00:21:23.050 align:middle line:10%
a peaceful world.

00:21:23.050 --> 00:21:25.840 align:middle line:10%
Whenever we face
some problem, we

00:21:25.840 --> 00:21:30.220 align:middle line:10%
must solve it through dialogue,
through peaceful means,

00:21:30.220 --> 00:21:32.320 align:middle line:10%
through non-violent ways.

00:21:32.320 --> 00:21:38.850 align:middle line:10%
So people should
know the real method

00:21:38.850 --> 00:21:45.950 align:middle line:10%
to get happy life,
not through money,

00:21:45.950 --> 00:21:52.268 align:middle line:10%
not through power, but through
honest, truthful compassion.

00:21:52.268 --> 00:21:55.761 align:middle line:90%
[SCRAPING]

00:21:55.761 --> 00:22:27.198 align:middle line:90%


00:22:27.198 --> 00:22:29.194 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

00:22:29.194 --> 00:22:43.700 align:middle line:90%


00:22:43.700 --> 00:22:45.330 align:middle line:10%
>> Where's the sand coming from?

00:22:45.330 --> 00:22:47.782 align:middle line:10%
>> The sand we
make by ourselves.

00:22:47.782 --> 00:22:50.870 align:middle line:10%
So this sand is from soft rock.

00:22:50.870 --> 00:22:53.100 align:middle line:10%
And then we crush
it and we wash it.

00:22:53.100 --> 00:22:54.690 align:middle line:10%
>> How do your crush it?

00:22:54.690 --> 00:22:57.430 align:middle line:10%
>> Like, with a hard
rock, with another rock.

00:22:57.430 --> 00:22:59.090 align:middle line:10%
>> Oh, you crush it like this?

00:22:59.090 --> 00:22:59.890 align:middle line:10%
>> Yes.

00:22:59.890 --> 00:23:02.700 align:middle line:10%
And then we wash it, and
mix it with the color.

00:23:02.700 --> 00:23:07.670 align:middle line:90%


00:23:07.670 --> 00:23:11.149 align:middle line:90%
[SCRAPING]

00:23:11.149 --> 00:23:19.600 align:middle line:90%


00:23:19.600 --> 00:23:22.150 align:middle line:10%
>> You don't have any
support or copy to do it?

00:23:22.150 --> 00:23:26.960 align:middle line:10%
>> Copy-- yeah, actually, before
we have to memorize this--

00:23:26.960 --> 00:23:29.155 align:middle line:10%
all the lines and
then the drawing.

00:23:29.155 --> 00:23:33.279 align:middle line:10%
We have to learn it before
drawing the mandala.

00:23:33.279 --> 00:23:34.570 align:middle line:10%
>> So you have it in your head?

00:23:34.570 --> 00:23:36.310 align:middle line:10%
>> Yes, we have to memorize it.

00:23:36.310 --> 00:23:37.274 align:middle line:10%
>> All the mandala?

00:23:37.274 --> 00:23:38.074 align:middle line:10%
>> Yes.

00:23:38.074 --> 00:23:40.150 align:middle line:10%
>> But there are
so many details.

00:23:40.150 --> 00:23:42.170 align:middle line:10%
>> Yes, it's actually
all written in scripture.

00:23:42.170 --> 00:23:44.242 align:middle line:10%
So if we can memorize
the scripture entirely,

00:23:44.242 --> 00:23:47.770 align:middle line:10%
then we can do it.

00:23:47.770 --> 00:23:50.630 align:middle line:10%
>> How are you chosen
to make the mandala?

00:23:50.630 --> 00:23:52.790 align:middle line:10%
>> Just, we write our
names on a paper--

00:23:52.790 --> 00:23:53.590 align:middle line:10%
>> And we draw it.

00:23:53.590 --> 00:23:54.390 align:middle line:10%
>> --all the monks.

00:23:54.390 --> 00:23:56.940 align:middle line:10%
And we just draw it, and
we pick it up like that.

00:23:56.940 --> 00:24:00.490 align:middle line:10%
>> Can all the monks put
a ticket to be chosen?

00:24:00.490 --> 00:24:02.340 align:middle line:10%
>> After completing
the memorizing class,

00:24:02.340 --> 00:24:05.180 align:middle line:10%
only then you have
to write your name.

00:24:05.180 --> 00:24:06.370 align:middle line:10%
>> How long is the class?

00:24:06.370 --> 00:24:06.940 align:middle line:10%
>> It depends.

00:24:06.940 --> 00:24:07.120 align:middle line:10%
From--

00:24:07.120 --> 00:24:07.780 align:middle line:10%
>> If you're very smart--

00:24:07.780 --> 00:24:08.580 align:middle line:10%
>> Just one year.

00:24:08.580 --> 00:24:09.970 align:middle line:10%
>> --yeah, finish in one year.

00:24:09.970 --> 00:24:10.440 align:middle line:10%
>> One and a half years.

00:24:10.440 --> 00:24:11.439 align:middle line:10%
>> One and a half years.

