So I listened to them.

00:47:32.300 --> 00:47:33.550 align:middle line:10%
>> You still want to be a nun?

00:47:33.550 --> 00:47:34.590 align:middle line:10%
>> Yes.

00:47:34.590 --> 00:47:37.860 align:middle line:84%
>> I thought you were
engaged to Jampa.

00:47:37.860 --> 00:47:39.997 align:middle line:10%
So you're still searching?

00:47:39.997 --> 00:47:42.330 align:middle line:10%
>> I really feel that way,
but I'm stuck between the two

00:47:42.330 --> 00:47:46.020 align:middle line:10%
decisions, you know, to become
a nun and live a completely

00:47:46.020 --> 00:47:50.770 align:middle line:10%
spiritual life, or to get
married and have children,

00:47:50.770 --> 00:47:53.590 align:middle line:10%
and a normal life.

00:47:53.590 --> 00:47:55.320 align:middle line:10%
>> Are there nunneries
in Dharamsala?

00:47:55.320 --> 00:47:58.210 align:middle line:10%
>> Yeah, there are almost
three, four nunneries.

00:47:58.210 --> 00:48:02.700 align:middle line:10%
In the history of Tibet,
the majority were monks.

00:48:02.700 --> 00:48:04.390 align:middle line:10%
But now things are changing.

00:48:04.390 --> 00:48:07.920 align:middle line:10%
And we can see more and
more Tibetan women studying

00:48:07.920 --> 00:48:09.790 align:middle line:10%
and practicing Buddhism.

00:48:09.790 --> 00:48:12.430 align:middle line:10%
And they are becoming
nuns as well.

00:48:12.430 --> 00:48:17.880 align:middle line:10%
And you can see more Tibetan
dharma institutes and nunneries

00:48:17.880 --> 00:48:18.715 align:middle line:10%
as well.

00:48:18.715 --> 00:48:22.180 align:middle line:90%
[GONG]

00:48:22.180 --> 00:48:41.485 align:middle line:90%


00:48:41.485 --> 00:48:44.950 align:middle line:90%
[CHANTING]

00:48:44.950 --> 00:49:46.806 align:middle line:90%


00:49:46.806 --> 00:49:50.292 align:middle line:90%
[CHATTER]

00:49:50.292 --> 00:50:20.180 align:middle line:90%


00:50:20.180 --> 00:51:34.616 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

00:51:34.616 --> 00:51:35.598 align:middle line:90%
[GONG]

00:51:35.598 --> 00:51:38.991 align:middle line:90%
[CHANTING]

00:51:38.991 --> 00:52:35.252 align:middle line:90%


00:52:35.252 --> 00:52:38.731 align:middle line:90%
[DRAMYINS]

00:52:38.731 --> 00:52:40.719 align:middle line:90%


00:52:40.719 --> 00:52:44.198 align:middle line:90%
[SINGING]

00:52:44.198 --> 00:53:17.070 align:middle line:90%


00:53:17.070 --> 00:55:01.255 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

00:55:01.255 --> 00:55:26.720 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

00:55:26.720 --> 00:55:29.900 align:middle line:84%
>> In this preparatory phase,
we first examine the results

00:55:29.900 --> 00:55:32.810 align:middle line:84%
of throwing sticks that
shows the types of obstacles

00:55:32.810 --> 00:55:36.590 align:middle line:84%
to overcome, and then continue
through the distribution

00:55:36.590 --> 00:55:40.700 align:middle line:84%
of consecrated blessed water,
which purifies the three gates

00:55:40.700 --> 00:55:44.540 align:middle line:84%
of the body, the
speech, and the mind.

00:55:44.540 --> 00:55:48.170 align:middle line:10%
Following the distribution
of kusha, two sprays of herbs

00:55:48.170 --> 00:55:51.080 align:middle line:10%
that purify all
negatives overnight

00:55:51.080 --> 00:55:52.490 align:middle line:10%
and clarify your dreams.

00:55:52.490 --> 00:55:56.760 align:middle line:90%


00:55:56.760 --> 00:56:37.600 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

00:56:37.600 --> 00:56:40.510 align:middle line:84%
>> Now we proceed to the
distribution of cord protection

00:56:40.510 --> 00:56:42.550 align:middle line:90%
with three knots.

00:56:42.550 --> 00:56:47.360 align:middle line:84%
It is red, symbolizing
Maitreya, the Buddha of love,

00:56:47.360 --> 00:56:51.140 align:middle line:84%
who protects you from all
evil thoughts, internally

00:56:51.140 --> 00:56:53.718 align:middle line:84%
and externally,
of all obstacles.

00:56:53.718 --> 00:56:56.590 align:middle line:90%


00:56:56.590 --> 00:57:22.420 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

00:57:22.420 --> 00:57:25.090 align:middle line:84%
>> Then, to remove all
obstacles up to the time

00:57:25.090 --> 00:57:27.750 align:middle line:84%
of the initiation,
before you sleep,

00:57:27.750 --> 00:57:30.865 align:middle line:84%
you will recite the mantra
protector of the six families.

00:57:30.865 --> 00:57:34.904 align:middle line:90%


00:57:34.904 --> 00:57:53.130 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

00:57:53.130 --> 00:57:56.212 align:middle line:90%
[CHANTING]

00:57:56.212 --> 00:58:31.072 align:middle line:90%


00:58:31.072 --> 00:58:34.230 align:middle line:84%
>> Ketzin's serenity
impresses me.

00:58:34.230 --> 00:58:38.440 align:middle line:84%
When I ask him, what
you want to do in life,

00:58:38.440 --> 00:58:44.150 align:middle line:84%
despite his young age, he simply
replies, be helpful to others,

00:58:44.150 --> 00:58:44.970 align:middle line:90%
be a good person.

00:58:44.970 --> 00:58:47.566 align:middle line:90%


00:58:47.566 --> 00:58:49.890 align:middle line:10%
>> It is good to do kora.

00:58:49.890 --> 00:58:52.940 align:middle line:10%
>> Yes, walking around the
monastery of His Holiness

00:58:52.940 --> 00:58:54.592 align:middle line:10%
the Dalai Lama, it's good.

00:58:54.592 --> 00:58:55.474 align:middle line:10%
>> Yeah.

00:58:55.474 --> 00:58:57.560 align:middle line:10%
>> How many times you do it?

00:58:57.560 --> 00:58:59.155 align:middle line:10%
>> Three times.

00:58:59.155 --> 00:59:00.270 align:middle line:10%
>> Three times a day?

00:59:00.270 --> 00:59:01.266 align:middle line:10%
>> Yeah.

00:59:01.266 --> 00:59:10.728 align:middle line:90%


00:59:10.728 --> 00:59:13.440 align:middle line:10%
Yesterday I dreamed
of Nechung Kuten-la.

00:59:13.440 --> 00:59:14.424 align:middle line:10%
>> The oracle?

00:59:14.424 --> 00:59:18.325 align:middle line:10%
>> Yeah, and also
of Palden Lhamo.

00:59:18.325 --> 00:59:19.200 align:middle line:10%
>> In the same dream?

00:59:19.200 --> 00:59:20.940 align:middle line:10%
>> Yes.

00:59:20.940 --> 00:59:23.400 align:middle line:10%
>> What did he do, the oracle?

00:59:23.400 --> 00:59:25.342 align:middle line:10%
>> He was in a trance.

00:59:25.342 --> 00:59:28.779 align:middle line:10%
[CHANTING]

00:59:28.779 --> 00:59:36.144 align:middle line:90%


00:59:36.144 --> 01:00:20.306 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

01:00:20.306 --> 01:00:23.778 align:middle line:90%
[TINGSHA]

01:00:23.778 --> 01:00:27.250 align:middle line:90%
[DRUMS]

01:00:27.250 --> 01:00:31.218 align:middle line:90%


01:00:31.218 --> 01:00:34.690 align:middle line:90%
[CHANTING]

01:00:34.690 --> 01:00:53.080 align:middle line:90%


01:00:53.080 --> 01:01:19.320 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

01:01:19.320 --> 01:01:22.170 align:middle line:84%
>> What was the
nature of your dreams?

01:01:22.170 --> 01:01:24.940 align:middle line:84%
If you have dreamt of a
spiritual master or Buddha,

01:01:24.940 --> 01:01:27.020 align:middle line:90%
it bodes well.

01:01:27.020 --> 01:01:31.030 align:middle line:10%
In this dimension of the dream,
you can see the clear light.

01:01:31.030 --> 01:01:32.820 align:middle line:84%
It is the true nature
of the mind that

01:01:32.820 --> 01:01:35.190 align:middle line:90%
appears at the moment of death.

01:01:35.190 --> 01:01:39.570 align:middle line:84%
It is pure consciousness,
without subject or object.

01:01:39.570 --> 01:01:41.750 align:middle line:84%
Training ourselves
by practicing dreams

01:01:41.750 --> 01:01:45.110 align:middle line:84%
allows us to recognize
this fundamental light

01:01:45.110 --> 01:01:47.740 align:middle line:84%
at the time of death,
and thus attain

01:01:47.740 --> 01:01:49.982 align:middle line:90%
the state of enlightenment.

01:01:49.982 --> 01:02:04.370 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

01:02:04.370 --> 01:02:08.390 align:middle line:84%
>> We are at the entrance
of the mandala, my palace.

01:02:08.390 --> 01:02:10.400 align:middle line:84%
Reaffirm your
commitment to attain

01:02:10.400 --> 01:02:14.740 align:middle line:84%
the perfect enlightenment
for the sake of all beings.

01:02:14.740 --> 01:02:17.270 align:middle line:84%
You will now lift the
veil of ignorance that

01:02:17.270 --> 01:02:21.370 align:middle line:90%
covers your unpurified mind.

01:02:21.370 --> 01:02:23.010 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

01:02:23.010 --> 01:03:20.480 align:middle line:90%


01:03:20.480 --> 01:03:23.250 align:middle line:10%
>> Purified, you then
enter, with eyes open,

01:03:23.250 --> 01:03:26.940 align:middle line:10%
into my supreme city of
the great liberation.

01:03:26.940 --> 01:03:30.540 align:middle line:10%
That is my mandala, with
five floors consisting

01:03:30.540 --> 01:03:35.160 align:middle line:10%
of a center, and outer circle,
and a periphery or four doors

01:03:35.160 --> 01:03:38.700 align:middle line:10%
whose colors are associated
with the cardinal directions,

01:03:38.700 --> 01:03:40.180 align:middle line:10%
and my four faces.

01:03:40.180 --> 01:03:48.210 align:middle line:90%


01:03:48.210 --> 01:03:53.010 align:middle line:84%
The mandala contains
722 deities.

01:03:53.010 --> 01:03:57.740 align:middle line:84%
We enter the body mandala,
then the mandala of speech,

01:03:57.740 --> 01:04:00.690 align:middle line:84%
then into the mandala
of mind, containing

01:04:00.690 --> 01:04:03.720 align:middle line:84%
the mandala of wisdom,
to reach the mandala

01:04:03.720 --> 01:04:09.852 align:middle line:84%
of bliss, where I remain with my
consort, my feminine principle.

01:04:09.852 --> 01:04:15.756 align:middle line:90%


01:04:15.756 --> 01:04:17.724 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

01:04:17.724 --> 01:04:55.730 align:middle line:90%


01:04:55.730 --> 01:04:58.440 align:middle line:84%
>> You have entered
the body mandala.

01:04:58.440 --> 01:05:00.530 align:middle line:84%
You are like a
newborn, and can now

01:05:00.530 --> 01:05:04.850 align:middle line:84%
receive the seven initiations
similar to events in childhood.

01:05:04.850 --> 01:05:08.154 align:middle line:90%
>> [CHANTING]

01:05:08.154 --> 01:05:11.930 align:middle line:90%


01:05:11.930 --> 01:05:14.930 align:middle line:84%
>> First, let's proceed
to the water initiation,

01:05:14.930 --> 01:05:19.110 align:middle line:84%
symbolizing the first bath the
mother gives to her newborn.

01:05:19.110 --> 01:05:21.590 align:middle line:84%
This is the purification
of the body.

01:05:21.590 --> 01:05:32.900 align:middle line:90%


01:05:32.900 --> 01:05:35.000 align:middle line:84%
Next is the crown
initiation, which

01:05:35.000 --> 01:05:39.440 align:middle line:84%
is associated to the first
haircut of the child.

01:05:39.440 --> 01:05:41.690 align:middle line:10%
The hair is sometimes
compared to thousands

01:05:41.690 --> 01:05:45.140 align:middle line:10%
of threads that bind us
to samsara that we cut

01:05:45.140 --> 01:05:47.990 align:middle line:10%
when taking the monastic vows.

01:05:47.990 --> 01:05:51.530 align:middle line:10%
This is how one is freed from
self-centered appropriation.

01:05:51.530 --> 01:06:03.000 align:middle line:90%


01:06:03.000 --> 01:06:05.620 align:middle line:84%
The silk ribbon
initiation, corresponding

01:06:05.620 --> 01:06:09.670 align:middle line:84%
with the development of the
embryo within the matrix--

01:06:09.670 --> 01:06:12.820 align:middle line:84%
it cleanses the psychophysical
defilements circulating

01:06:12.820 --> 01:06:15.130 align:middle line:90%
in our subtle system.

01:06:15.130 --> 01:06:19.210 align:middle line:84%
It is associated with the act
of piercing the ears of a child,

01:06:19.210 --> 01:06:20.680 align:middle line:90%
giving their first jewelry.

01:06:20.680 --> 01:06:24.000 align:middle line:90%


01:06:24.000 --> 01:06:26.380 align:middle line:10%
The Vajra and bell
initiation corresponds

01:06:26.380 --> 01:06:28.960 align:middle line:10%
to when the child begins
to laugh and articulate

01:06:28.960 --> 01:06:32.230 align:middle line:10%
sounds, allowing them
the ability to achieve,

01:06:32.230 --> 01:06:36.070 align:middle line:10%
in the future, the
enlightened word of Buddha.

01:06:36.070 --> 01:06:38.440 align:middle line:10%
In the last three
initiations, the one

01:06:38.440 --> 01:06:41.050 align:middle line:10%
of the conduct
initiation correlates

01:06:41.050 --> 01:06:43.510 align:middle line:10%
to the first pleasures
a child takes

01:06:43.510 --> 01:06:46.690 align:middle line:10%
in the discovery of the
world of the senses.

01:06:46.690 --> 01:06:48.760 align:middle line:10%
You are qualified
to have the right

01:06:48.760 --> 01:06:53.200 align:middle line:10%
to conduct and use objects
without any attachments.

01:06:53.200 --> 01:06:55.990 align:middle line:10%
The name initiation
corresponds to the name

01:06:55.990 --> 01:06:57.910 align:middle line:10%
that the child receives.

01:06:57.910 --> 01:07:01.350 align:middle line:10%
It purifies the
faculties of action.

01:07:01.350 --> 01:07:04.600 align:middle line:10%
Last, the permission
initiation corresponds

01:07:04.600 --> 01:07:08.190 align:middle line:10%
to the first reading
lesson of the child.

01:07:08.190 --> 01:07:27.570 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

01:07:27.570 --> 01:07:30.720 align:middle line:10%
>> During the initiation,
the Dalai Lama continuously

01:07:30.720 --> 01:07:36.190 align:middle line:10%
repeats, "Give, give without
waiting for anything in return.

01:07:36.190 --> 01:07:40.590 align:middle line:84%
You will receive so much
more than what you gave."

01:07:40.590 --> 01:07:43.980 align:middle line:84%
I gave a leaf of the Bodhi
tree, the tree under which

01:07:43.980 --> 01:07:45.930 align:middle line:90%
the Buddha awakened.

01:07:45.930 --> 01:07:48.800 align:middle line:90%
I have received so much more.

01:07:48.800 --> 01:07:51.785 align:middle line:84%
When I have no expectations,
the surprises multiply.

01:07:51.785 --> 01:07:55.460 align:middle line:90%


01:07:55.460 --> 01:07:59.600 align:middle line:84%
My obsessive quest for happiness
dissipates little by little.

01:07:59.600 --> 01:08:02.988 align:middle line:84%
When I follow the flow
of life, I feel peaceful.

01:08:02.988 --> 01:09:07.660 align:middle line:90%


01:09:07.660 --> 01:10:23.558 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

01:10:23.558 --> 01:10:27.044 align:middle line:10%
[BELL RINGING]

01:10:27.044 --> 01:10:47.490 align:middle line:90%


01:10:47.490 --> 01:11:28.290 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

01:11:28.290 --> 01:11:33.150 align:middle line:84%
>> On the oracle's advice
Tenzin traveled to [INAUDIBLE]

01:11:33.150 --> 01:11:37.080 align:middle line:84%
to clear away her
doubts and confusion.

01:11:37.080 --> 01:11:44.200 align:middle line:84%
Her beauty and delicacy
touched me as a sister would,

01:11:44.200 --> 01:11:45.000 align:middle line:90%
my sister.

01:11:45.000 --> 01:11:58.580 align:middle line:90%


01:11:58.580 --> 01:12:00.020 align:middle line:90%
Which path will she take?

01:12:00.020 --> 01:12:03.550 align:middle line:90%


01:12:03.550 --> 01:12:07.229 align:middle line:10%
Whatever she decides, it
will be the path of love.

01:12:07.229 --> 01:12:48.147 align:middle line:90%


01:12:48.147 --> 01:12:51.640 align:middle line:90%
[APPLAUSE]

01:12:51.640 --> 01:13:08.606 align:middle line:90%


01:13:08.606 --> 01:13:12.099 align:middle line:90%
[CHANTING]

01:13:12.099 --> 01:13:28.860 align:middle line:90%


01:13:28.860 --> 01:13:50.690 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

01:13:50.690 --> 01:13:53.930 align:middle line:84%
>> We conclude with the
initiation of the Vajra master,

01:13:53.930 --> 01:13:56.734 align:middle line:84%
transmitted through
the initiation vase,

01:13:56.734 --> 01:14:01.210 align:middle line:84%
symbolizing achievement and lack
of differentiation of the body,

01:14:01.210 --> 01:14:04.710 align:middle line:84%
the speech, and the
mind in a unique flavor.

01:14:04.710 --> 01:14:09.344 align:middle line:90%


01:14:09.344 --> 01:14:11.070 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

01:14:11.070 --> 01:14:49.110 align:middle line:90%


01:14:49.110 --> 01:15:27.780 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

01:15:27.780 --> 01:15:31.560 align:middle line:84%
>> Now, let yourself
feel divine pride.

01:15:31.560 --> 01:15:33.930 align:middle line:90%
I am Kalachakra.

01:15:33.930 --> 01:15:38.730 align:middle line:84%
I am the non-time that includes
the three times, past, present,

01:15:38.730 --> 01:15:40.170 align:middle line:90%
and future.

01:15:40.170 --> 01:15:42.540 align:middle line:84%
There is neither
beginning nor end.

01:15:42.540 --> 01:15:45.360 align:middle line:84%
Birth and death, the
beginning and the end,

01:15:45.360 --> 01:15:47.820 align:middle line:90%
seem opposite in appearance.

01:15:47.820 --> 01:15:49.710 align:middle line:90%
However, there is continuity.

01:15:49.710 --> 01:15:53.100 align:middle line:84%
Integrate these
opposites, and live fully.

01:15:53.100 --> 01:15:54.420 align:middle line:90%
Fight ignorance.

01:15:54.420 --> 01:15:56.670 align:middle line:90%
Cultivate enlightenment.

01:15:56.670 --> 01:16:00.090 align:middle line:84%
My wish is that all
of you become Buddhas.

01:16:00.090 --> 01:16:02.580 align:middle line:84%
And by the power
of this initiation,

01:16:02.580 --> 01:16:07.080 align:middle line:84%
it is certain that one day,
sooner or later, each of you

01:16:07.080 --> 01:16:10.290 align:middle line:90%
will become a Buddha.

01:16:10.290 --> 01:16:12.230 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

01:16:12.230 --> 01:16:14.044 align:middle line:10%


01:16:14.044 --> 01:16:17.460 align:middle line:10%
[APPLAUSE]

01:16:17.460 --> 01:16:47.320 align:middle line:90%


01:16:47.320 --> 01:16:52.060 align:middle line:84%
>> My children, my
family, they are alive.

01:16:52.060 --> 01:16:53.690 align:middle line:90%
It's time to go home.

01:16:53.690 --> 01:16:56.080 align:middle line:90%
I want to live.

01:16:56.080 --> 01:18:54.040 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

01:18:54.040 --> 01:18:56.024 align:middle line:10%
>> [SPEAKING TIBETAN]

01:18:56.024 --> 01:19:38.440 align:middle line:90%


01:19:38.440 --> 01:19:43.170 align:middle line:84%
>> Sooner or later, we will
all die, some too early.

01:19:43.170 --> 01:19:49.060 align:middle line:84%
This is the mystery of life, the
mystery of time, impermanence.

01:19:49.060 --> 01:19:51.730 align:middle line:90%
Nothing lasts forever.

01:19:51.730 --> 01:19:57.380 align:middle line:84%
The destruction of the mandala
symbolizes this so well.

01:19:57.380 --> 01:19:59.630 align:middle line:84%
Ketzin takes me, with
his young friend,

01:19:59.630 --> 01:20:02.210 align:middle line:84%
to a secret place where
he likes to seek refuge

01:20:02.210 --> 01:20:05.720 align:middle line:90%
from the world and meditate.

01:20:05.720 --> 01:20:08.150 align:middle line:90%
Nobody is forcing me to suffer.

01:20:08.150 --> 01:20:11.660 align:middle line:84%
No good can come out of
it, neither for my sister,

01:20:11.660 --> 01:20:12.990 align:middle line:90%
nor for me.

01:20:12.990 --> 01:20:14.450 align:middle line:90%
This is clear.

01:20:14.450 --> 01:20:16.940 align:middle line:90%
It is time for me to accept--

01:20:16.940 --> 01:20:18.770 align:middle line:90%
to accept.

01:20:18.770 --> 01:20:22.770 align:middle line:84%
Her existence is not confined
to a physical existence.

01:20:22.770 --> 01:20:25.830 align:middle line:90%
She appears in so many ways.

